message: Added package.json and version for work with npm install
Change keywords
bumped version
lower version
remove peer dependencies
update version
refactored repo to have ios and android folders at the root
merge pull request
version 0.13.6
added xcodeporj
changed native module name from UIImagePickerManager to ImagePickerManager
new cross-platform example project on RN 0.21
Merge branch 'master' of github.com:marcshilling/react-native-image-picker
version 0.18.16
add tiny js index file as to not have to deal with NativeModules directly
some tweaks. update to 0.19.8
use prepublish script to exclude the build folder. Delete .npmignore
support for RN 0.33 with backwards compatibility
update prepublish script
added typescript typing definition (#375)
Removed Logs
Update package.json
Cleaned up showImagePicker logic
fix name conflict

[ANDROID] Refactoring of Code plus bug fixes (#496)

* Fixed issue#485
Fixed issue#478

* Removed useless file

* Recoverd options for launchCamera and launchImageLibrary
Fixed dependencies (#504)
bump package version number
bump package version number
Bump version to 0.26.10
add license to package.json (#935)

Merge pull request #937 from react-community/master

Merge master into develop
Configure Prettier (#945)

Fix flow (#947)

* Fix Flow

* Add CircleCI config
Update podspec (#948)

V1.0.1 (#1120)

refactor: Replace JavaScript with TypeScript and AndroidX support
Code cleanup and api changes (#1422)
refactor(image-picker): additional refactoring
docs(contributors): update contributors
feat(typescript): convert to typescript (#1450)
feat(example): update example styling (#1469)
